descriptionHtml:
1.8 update: Created navmesh for followers/spouses to enter house. Smith shop on floor one modified.


A grand estate & elite architecture of Solitude in the heart of the Autumn, Rifthold woods surrounded by mountains and nestled next to the soothing sounds of a waterfall. This location is superb for hunting, fishing, dragon fighting, camping and riding horseback. Enhanced with a blacksmith station on floor one and a 2 horse stable in the side yard. Luxurious appointments by the best craftsmen in Solitude, imported to this rural location in the midst of countryside bliss. A convenient  map marker marks your way to your new home. Don\'t miss it this one will go fast!
author: Lainey
